---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - TaxPortal" description="TaxPortal privacy policy. Learn how we protect your data and ensure your privacy.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-canvas dark:bg-primary">
    <main class="min-h-screen">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary" data-i18n="privacy.title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-body dark:text-muted">
          <p data-i18n="privacy.intro">
            TaxPortal does not require you to create an account or provide personal information to use our calculators and guides. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary" data-i18n="privacy.calculations_local">Calculations Performed Locally</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.no_personal_data">
            All tax calculations are performed directly in your browser. No calculation data is sent to our servers or stored anywhere.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary" data-i18n="privacy.cookies">Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.cookies_detail">
            We use local storage only to remember your language preference and theme choice. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary" data-i18n="privacy.third_party">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.third_party_detail">
            Our site contains links to official government tax authority websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of external sites.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary" data-i18n="about.contact_us">Contact Us</h2>
          <p data-i18n="privacy.contact_detail">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out through our contact channels.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
